  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_e2f9a37755720fcc90afcff77f13640b">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Paper by Mary Ann P. Cofrin titled "An Exploration of the Factors that Lead to Lesbian Relationship Dissolution", also material regarding health issues and other resources.</p>  </scopecontent>
